{{> header}}
        <div class="page-header">
            <div class="header-container">
                <h1><i class="fa fa-user-circle-o fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i> Sign in</h1>
                <div class="description"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="body-container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="content-box content-box-default">
                        <div class="content-box-heading">
                            <h3><i class="fa fa-sign-in fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i> Sign in</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-box-body">
                            <form action="#" method="POST">
                                <input type="text" name="user" placeholder="Username" required="true">
                                <input type="password" name="pass" placeholder="Password" required="true">
                                <hr></hr>
                                <input type="checkbox">Remember me</input>
                                <button type="submit">Sign in</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="content-box content-box-default">
                        <div class="content-box-heading">
                            <h3><i class="fa fa-coffee fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i> Welcome Back!</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="content-box-body">
                            <p>
                                Hey there! It's been a bit, hasn't it?
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Sign on in and we'll fetch your info and send you on
                                your way.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Do you have no idea why we're saying this greeting? You must be new 
                                around here! In which case, why don't you head on over to the
                                <a href="/register">Registration page</a> and sign on up. It's free! 
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                And best of all you get access to nifty features like:
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Creating a reviewing or prereading group with likeminded people</li>
                                    <li>Striking out on your own and open your own reviewing workshop</li>
                                    <li>Submiting your story to the many groups we feature</li>
                                    <li>   
                                        Competing against your friends and fellow site members through various ego-stroking
                                        vanity projects
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                And so much more!
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                And as always, keep your wits sharp, and your pen at the ready.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                &#151;The Abstract Team
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
{{> footer}}